subject: Re: New Software Project
msgSnippet: Thanks for the interest. My studies have pulled me away from the project for a while, and my own programming skills are not yet enough to create worthwhile
messageBody:
Thanks for the interest. My studies have pulled me away from the project for a while, and my own programming skills are not yet enough to create worthwhile code. If you want to help I will gladly send you an invitation to the project.

Thanks,
Tim

> This sounds like a fun project, and I would like to join. However, the project at source forge seems empty. Has the project been abandoned?
>
